These are “Triggers” in Jenkins — they decide when your build should start automatically.
Let’s break each one in simple terms 👇

| Trigger              | When it runs      | Best use          |
| -------------------- | ----------------- | ----------------- |
| After other projects | After another job | Pipeline chaining |
| Build periodically   | On schedule       | Nightly jobs      |
| GitHub hook          | On code push      | CI/CD (best)      |
| Poll SCM             | Checks repeatedly | Backup method     |
| Remote trigger       | API/URL call      | Automation        |
